An alien creature floats in space in what appears to be a biological life-pod. It pulses with bioluminescent patterns — perhaps a language?

* [Bring it aboard and try to help]
  ~ gain_crew_member
  生物 (shēngwù) — creature
* [Study its bioluminescent patterns]
  ~ gain_radical("光")
  发光 (fāguāng) — glow
* [Leave it be — alien biology is unpredictable]
  ~ nothing
  未知 (wèizhī) — unknown
